{
    "name": "Fútbol"
}

### Crear Tag: Basketball
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/tags
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Basketball"
}

### Obtener Tag 1 (ajusta ID según corresponda)
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/tags/5
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1

### Actualizar Tag 1
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:3000/tags/6
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Fútbol Internacional"
}



# =========================================================================
# 3. REVIEWS (DEPORTES) + INTEGRIDAD CON TAGS
# =========================================================================

### Crear Review: Opinión deportiva usando Tag 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/reviews
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Opinión sobre la Champions League 2025",
    "description": "Análisis de equipos, rendimiento y predicciones.",
    "due_date": "2025-11-15",
    "owner": 1, 
    "tags": [1],  
    "rating": 9
}

### Intentar eliminar Tag 1 (DEBE FALLAR)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:3000/tags/1
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1

### Actualizar Review 1 (ajusta ID después)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:3000/reviews/6
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Opinión actualizada después de los octavos.",
    "rating": 7
}

### Eliminar Review 1
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:3000/reviews/6
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1

### Ahora sí: Eliminar Tag 1
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:3000/tags/6
x-auth: SuperPassDeportes#1



